Usage: detachTerm [-help] <instName> <termName> [<netName>]
                  [-moduleBased <moduleName>]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
<instName>                    # Name of instance (string, required)
<termName>                    # Name of Term (string, required)
<netName>                     # Name of Net (string, optional)
-moduleBased <moduleName>     # Name of verilog module (string, optional)